<plot>After fifty years, Grammy May gets a call from her old flame, prompting four generations of women to confront the costs of waiting for Mr Right. Is it a dream, or true love? Does love ever die, or do we die inside waiting for it? "For the Love of May" explores women's desire for the Right One to come along... or come back.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?200119</url></doc>
